#
#   running tests:
#
#   - on Linux, set LD_LIBRARY_PATH
#   - OS X, set DYLD_LIBRARY_PATH
#
#   Like so:
#   $ export DYLD_LIBRARY_PATH=../lib
#
#
#   Set LC_ALL:
#
#   $ export LC_ALL=en_US.utf8
#
#
#   Run tests:
#
#   $ ./testString
#
#   You should be able to see some Chinese/Japanese characters in the terminal
#   if the character sets are installed on your OS
#
